The paper deals with the analysis of scheduling policies in a polling system, which is a type of queueing system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT) as it considers the worst-case analysis of online scheduling policies. The paper also involves control theory (cs.SY) as it studies the behavior of a system under different policies. The paper also involves probability theory (cs.PF) as it deals with stochastic processes. Finally, the paper involves optimization (cs.MA) as it aims to find the best scheduling policy that minimizes the competitive ratio.
